snippet.title: Sean Lock: Our Favourite Moments
snippet.description:
Sean Lock never failed to make us laugh out loud. Picking his best bits is almost impossible, so just try and watch this without cracking up.

SUBSCRIBE: https://bit.ly/2v2I6SY 
 
About #Channel4: 
Welcome to Channel 4’s YouTube channel – a page jam-packed with clips from much-loved classics like Peep Show and The Great British Bake Off, and new hits like We Are Lady Parts and It’s A Sin. 

Whether you want to investigate the latest Dispatches, laugh your socks off at The Inbetweeners, or snuggle up on the sofa with your favourite Goggleboxers, there’s something for everyone right here.
